                <DIV class="ReviewHeading">Book Description:</DIV>
                <span id="Label1"><P>Experience the infinite variety of New Zealand:  Sample the caf&#233;s and bars of Auckland, take a gravity-defying bungy jump pr tramp through some of the world's most spectacular wilderness areas with this bestselling guidebook. <ul><li>over 120 detailed maps </li><li>colourful guide to New Zealand's unique wildlife </li><li>special section on Maori culture and art </li><li>fully extreme Activities chapter &#150; don't zorb without it </li><li>insider tips for an aspiring hobbit spotters </li><li>exhaustively researched accommodation listings </li></ul></span>
              
